text: First u screw up the delivery of my package.  Then u "invite" me to pick it up at the station.  Now at the station this...13 people in line,  not a single customer service agent in sight!!! #dobetter #whathappenedtocustomerservice?? @FedEx @FedExHelp https://t.co/nC6rgTXVyA

@AngBordenave Hello Angie, my name is Rebecca.  On behalf of FedEx, I apologize for any inconvenience or frustration that may have been caused by this matter.  Hi, this is Rebecca. May I look into this for you?  Please DM your address, tracking number, and phone number.
Thank you.
